'''Hayesville High School''' is a school located in [[Hayesville, North Carolina]]. According to their website, they have a current enrollment of 400 students<ref>http://www.clayschools.org/</ref> and 37 teaching staff members. That is an average of 10.8 students per teacher. <ref>http://www.hayesvillehs.org/faculty_staff/</ref>
